Welcome to the Crash Game Demo! This is a simple web-based game where you can place bets, watch a plane take off, and cash out before it crashes. The goal is to maximize your winnings by cashing out at the right moment.
Features

    Dynamic Multipliers: The game features random multipliers that can go up to 20x, making it exciting and unpredictable.
    Betting System: Players can set their bet amounts and see potential winnings based on the multiplier.
    Game History: Keep track of your last games, including bets, wins, and crash points.
    Interactive Gameplay: Enjoy a simple user interface with animated elements.
